Upstream project
----------------

This repository is derived from the Home Assistant custom integration maintained
by **Yusuf Nayab** as **qld_fuel-hass** (Queensland mandatory fuel price
reporting API integration):

  https://github.com/spusuf/qld_fuel-hass

The starting point for this codebase was upstream **release v.2.0.0** (zone-based
tracking and multiple instances):

  https://github.com/spusuf/qld_fuel-hass/releases/tag/v.2.0.0

This project continues development under a different integration domain
(`qld_servo_price`) and repository. Feature set, quality targets, and packaging
may diverge from upstream.

The upstream project and its contributors are not affiliated with this
repository unless they choose to participate here. See LICENSE and git history
for license text and contribution lineage.
